summary: This video showcases a variety of steak dishes and drinks at a Muslim-owned HALAL steakhouse. It features a premium meat platter, Angus short ribs with mash, truffle mushroom pasta with ribeye steak, oyster blade steak with fried rice, and a Banjir cheese burger. The video also shows drinks like a pink beverage and a lychee-based cocktail.
on_screen_text: This Muslim-owned HALAL steakhouse is a MUST try
- Truffle Mushroom Pasta with Ribeye Steak
- Oyster Blade Steak with Fried Rice
